        <title>AXLE ALIGNMENT WITH FRAME</title>
        <para>After determining that the frame is properly aligned, the axle alignment with the frame should be checked
            by comparing diagonals.
        </para>
        <para>If necessary, adjust axle-to-frame alignment. Refer to GROUP 03 - SUSPENSION in the CTS-5000 Master
            Service Manual.
        </para>
